## Lead Generation Outreach — Detail

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Trigger
    participant Enrich as Enrichment API
    participant AI as GPT-4.1
    participant CRM as Sheets/CRM
    participant Send as SendGrid/Gmail
    
    Trigger->>Enrich: {email/domain} → Company, Role, Tech Stack, Size
    Enrich-->>AI: Enriched Lead Profile
    AI->>AI: Generate Personalized Sequence (3-5 touches)
    AI-->>CRM: Log Lead + Sequence + Status="Pending"
    AI->>Send: Touch 1 (Email/LinkedIn)
    Send-->>CRM: Update Status="Sent", Track Opens/Clicks
    Note over CRM: Wait 3 days → Touch 2 → Wait 5 days → Touch 3
```

### Enrichment Data Points
| Category | Fields |
|----------|--------|
| **Company** | Name, Domain, Industry, Size, Revenue, Location, Tech Stack |
| **Contact** | Name, Title, Seniority, Department, LinkedIn, Verified Email |
| **Intent** | Topic Interest, Recent Funding, Hiring, Tech Changes |

### AI Sequence Template
```json
{
  "touches": [
    {"day": 0, "channel": "email", "template": "value_first"},
    {"day": 3, "channel": "email", "template": "case_study"},
    {"day": 8, "channel": "linkedin", "template": "soft_touch"},
    {"day": 14, "channel": "email", "template": "breakup"}
  ],
  "personalization": ["company_name", "role", "pain_point", "competitor_mention"]
}
```

