## E-Commerce Inventory — Detail

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Cron
    participant API as Shopify/WooCommerce
    participant Check as Conditional
    participant Alert as Slack/Email/SMS
    participant Reorder as PO/Supplier
    participant Log as Sheets
    
    Cron->>API: GET /inventory?updated_since=1h
    API-->>Check: Variant Stock Levels
    Check->>Check: stock < reorder_point?
    Check-->>Alert: low_stock items → #inventory-alerts
    Check-->>Reorder: auto-create PO for vendor
    Check-->>Log: {sku, stock, action, timestamp}
    Note over Log: Historical trend → demand forecasting
```

### Inventory Rules
| Metric | Threshold | Action |
|--------|-----------|--------|
| **Stock Level** | < Reorder Point | Alert + Auto-Reorder |
| **Stock Level** | = 0 | Urgent Alert + Expedite PO |
| **Velocity** | > 30 days supply | Reduce Reorder Qty |
| **Velocity** | < 7 days supply | Increase Reorder Qty |
| **Seasonal** | Known peaks | Pre-load Safety Stock |

