## Email Marketing — Detail

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Trigger
    participant Segment as CRM/Sheets
    participant AI as GPT-4.1
    participant Send as SendGrid/Mailchimp
    participant Analytics as Sheets
    
    Trigger->>Segment: Query: active_subscribers + segments
    Segment-->>AI: {segment, behavior, demographics}
    AI->>AI: Personalize Subject + Body + CTA per Segment
    AI-->>Send: Campaign {list, template, variables}
    Send-->>Analytics: {send_id, delivered, opens, clicks}
    Note over Analytics: Webhook → Update per-contact metrics
```

### Segmentation Matrix
| Segment | Criteria | Personalization |
|---------|----------|-----------------|
| **New Subscribers** | < 30 days, no purchase | Welcome series, education |
| **Active Buyers** | > 1 purchase, < 90 days | Cross-sell, loyalty |
| **At Risk** | > 90 days, no engagement | Win-back, offer |
| **VIP** | > 3 purchases OR > $500 LTV | Exclusive, early access |
| **Cart Abandoners** | Cart value > $50, < 24h | Recovery + incentive |

