## Scaling Business Automation

| Dimension | Current | Scaling Path |
|-----------|---------|--------------|
| **Leads/Month** | ~500 | Batch enrichment, parallel AI sequences |
| **SKUs Monitored** | ~200 | Incremental sync, change detection |
| **Email Volume** | ~10K/mo | SendGrid dedicated IP, reputation mgmt |
| **Segments** | 5-7 | ML-based clustering (RFM, behavioral) |
| **Channels** | Email + Slack | SMS, WhatsApp, Push, In-App |
| **Attribution** | Last-click | Multi-touch (UTM + CRM + GA) |
| **Testing** | Manual A/B | Automated multi-arm bandit |